 public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"4qcpj-0-0\"><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"4qcpj-0-0\">Affordable online education has become a favorite way for employees and entrepreneurs alike to up skill</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"4qcpj-1-0\">. As the trend grows, the options available grows too. Finding the right online education for the position you\'re looking for is important. We\'ll help guide you through some affordable education options! </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"83rfi-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"83rfi-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"83rfi-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"bmbla-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"bmbla-0-0\">Affordable Online Education Options</span></h2>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"51q2h-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"51q2h-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-0-0\">There are many college options outside of the traditional 4-year campus education. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-1-0\">Most online education programs </span></span><span class=\"passivevoice\"><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-2-0\">are advertised</span></span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-3-0\"> to adult students who weren’t able to start college after high school</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-4-0\">. Or who were unable to finish due to family responsibilities or financial strains. But, online education is a great way for </span><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-4-1\">anyone</span><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-4-2\"> to further their education. One of the highest rated online bachelor\'s programs is Penn State World Campus. Less than 10% enrolled are ‘traditional students’ fresh out of high school! </span><span class=\"veryhardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-5-0\">The growing amount of college courses available, including iTunes U &amp; MIT’s open course ware, make online learning a possibility for everyone</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"51q2h-6-0\">.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"avq57-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"avq57-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"avq57-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h2 data-offset-key=\"avq57-0-0\">Online Degree Program</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"5dis5-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"5dis5-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-0-0\">An online degree program is a perfect option for students who can’t attend college on campus. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-1-0\">Because of responsibilities such as family commitments or the need to work a full-time job to stay </span></span><span class=\"adverb\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-2-0\">financially</span></span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-3-0\"> stable</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-4-0\">. The best online schools allow for a lot of interaction with other students. Options exist such as online forums, emails, or working on group projects over the phone. To succeed in an online learning program, though, you must be a self-motivated student. Because there’s no one watching over you to make sure that you do your assignments and hand in your homework on time. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-5-0\">Anyone can become self-motivated due to the financial commitment that’s involved with an education</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-6-0\">! A financial commitment is enough to motivate </span><span class=\"qualifier\"><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-7-0\">just</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5dis5-8-0\"> about anyone.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"fuh9m-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"fuh9m-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"fuh9m-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h3 data-offset-key=\"fuh9m-0-0\">A Great Combination of Affordable and Flexible</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"brumc-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"brumc-0-0\"><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"brumc-0-0\">Online programs are so wonderful because they not only present a much cheaper way to get an education</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"brumc-1-0\">. They also offer an flexible way to receive a high-quality education. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"brumc-2-0\">To find the most affordable online education possible, you should first explore financial aid options</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"brumc-3-0\">.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"4n3ak-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"4n3ak-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"4n3ak-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h2 data-offset-key=\"4n3ak-0-0\">Financial Aid Options</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"c35oq-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"c35oq-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"c35oq-0-0\">First, find out what the school’s financial aid application process is. Usually, there will be a whole section devoted to this on the school’s website.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"829nf-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"829nf-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"829nf-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-0-0\"><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-0-0\">There is also a process called a “financial appeal”, which you would do if you get awarded an amount of financial aid but still can’t afford school</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-1-0\">. If this happens, you’ll have to contact the school’s financial aid officer. Private colleges are often in a better situation to adjust a financial aid award than a state school. When reaching out, you will have to tell them what your financial situation is. Tell them what is preventing you from being able to pay for school. Talk about your family’s financial situation. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-2-0\">Especially if it is a difficult situation that is contributing to your inability to pay for school</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"2p8ps-3-0\">.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"3cq71-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"3cq71-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"3cq71-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h3 data-offset-key=\"3cq71-0-0\">Healthy Competition Can Help You</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"76dd0-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"76dd0-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"76dd0-0-0\">You can also show the school that you’ve received other financial aid offers, in a diplomatic way. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"76dd0-1-0\">If you show them that you want to attend their school, they may be open to negotiating your financial award to compete with other schools</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"76dd0-2-0\">.</span></div>\n<div data-offset-key=\"76dd0-0-0\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"282cm-0-0\">\n<h2 class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"282cm-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"282cm-0-0\">Remote Education Can Be Difficult </span></h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"d6jkb-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"d6jkb-0-0\"><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"d6jkb-0-0\">Before you start the application process, you should know that it’s not any easier to earn a degree online than on a campus school</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"d6jkb-1-0\">. Prepare yourself to work hard! There are certain challenges that come along with online education. Some may find that it’s harder to stay engaged in your studies. There’s no one reminding you when your assignments are due. Online education isn’t for everyone.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"43sc3-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"43sc3-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"43sc3-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h3 data-offset-key=\"43sc3-0-0\">The Risk is Often Worth the Reward</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-0-0\">But, online learning is a great way to further your education. Stay aware of all the financial obligations associated. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-1-0\">Understand that there are financial regulations that can determine the amount of loan money you get</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-2-0\">. Also understand when you will have to repay your loans. </span><span class=\"hardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-3-0\">You should look at the entire educational experience, and understand what it will cost you into the future</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"a9fq8-4-0\">. By furthering your education, you are investing in yourself. As you would with any other investment, it’s crucial to have a full understanding of the costs involved.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"7pkkv-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"7pkkv-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"7pkkv-0-0\"> </span></div>\n<h2 data-offset-key=\"7pkkv-0-0\">Be Aware of the Costs and Don\'t Apply to Schools that You Can\'t Afford!</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"be9sq-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"be9sq-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"be9sq-0-0\">At some larger schools, online programs are not a very big part of their total course offerings. You may not be able to receive financial aid. But, there are so many schools that do offer generous financial aid, you should be able to find one! Always be smart, and ask the right questions before you apply. Don’t waste time applying to schools you won’t be able to afford.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"anucq-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"anucq-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"anucq-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"5lfng-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"5lfng-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-0-0\">Sometimes, online degree programs will offer specific scholarships for adult students! </span><span class=\"complexword\"><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-1-0\">However</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-2-0\">, it’s always important to do your research. </span><span class=\"veryhardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-3-0\">The government regulations that apply to federal financial aid programs ensure that schools include all associated costs in their cost of attendance</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-4-0\">. </span><span class=\"complexword\"><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-5-0\">However</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"5lfng-6-0\">, online schools don’t have these costs! Make sure you are borrowing only enough money to pay for the costs of your education. Over-borrowing is dangerous! You don’t want to have to pay back money you don’t need. </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"ao4fm-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"ao4fm-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"ao4fm-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<h2 class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"2hg2b-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"2hg2b-0-0\">Non-traditional Affordable Online Education</span></h2>\n<h3 class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"c7s85-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"c7s85-0-0\">Bootcamps</span></h3>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-0-0\">Bootcamps are almost always technology related. And they\'re not exactly cheap. </span><span class=\"complexword\"><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-1-0\">However</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-2-0\">, many have a proven track record of landing their graduates high-paying jobs. Some only charge </span><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-2-1\">after</span><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-2-2\"> you\'ve found employment in the field you studied for. Here\'s a options few that are </span><span class=\"adverb\"><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-3-0\">widely</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"b2rpn-4-0\"> regarded as good bootcamp options:</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"3vv3o-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"3vv3o-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"3vv3o-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<ol>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"278so-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"278so-0-0\"><a href=\"https://www.hackreactor.com/remote-immersive\">Hack Reactor Remote</a></span></li>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"278so-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"7155u-0-0\"><a href=\"https://www.fullstackacademy.com/remote-immersive\">Fullstack Academy Remote</a></span></li>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"278so-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"3vjk7-0-0\"><a href=\"https://flatironschool.com/\">Flatiron School</a></span></li>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"278so-0-0\"><a href=\"https://generalassemb.ly/\"><span data-offset-key=\"a4h9k-0-0\">General Assembly</span></a></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"2ge4-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"2ge4-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"2ge4-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"2b09b-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"2b09b-0-0\"><span class=\"veryhardreadability\"><span data-offset-key=\"2b09b-0-0\">Bootcamps are a fantastic option for affordable online education, but they\'re usually technology related</span></span><span data-offset-key=\"2b09b-1-0\">. We understand that not everyone has an interest in working at a computer all day. Here\'s some other options if you\'re looking for less technology-oriented courses. </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"c7fnn-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"c7fnn-0-0\"></div>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"dc6sa-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"dc6sa-0-0\">Certification Schools</span></h3>\n<ol>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"3p8m8-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"3p8m8-0-0\"><a href=\"https://www.nyicd.edu/\">New York Institute of Career Development</a></span></li>\n 	<li class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"3p8m8-0-0\"><a href=\"https://www.pennfoster.edu/\"><span data-offset-key=\"ub3n-0-0\">PennFoster</span></a></li>\n 	<li data-offset-key=\"3p8m8-0-0\"><a href=\"https://www.ashworthcollege.edu/\"><span data-offset-key=\"eihtl-0-0\">Ashworth College</span></a></li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"3g43r-0-0\">\n<div class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" data-offset-key=\"3g43r-0-0\"><span data-offset-key=\"3g43r-0-0\"> </span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"flmcv\" data-offset-key=\"8i2f4-