uestions depending on the product and the company.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2. Event Planner</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>Event planning certification (can be obtained via online courses)<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$22 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Event planning is one of the most <em>interesting</em> and <em>rewarding</em> work from home opportunities. You need an event planning certification, but there are plenty of viable online courses where you can obtain one in a few short weeks.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This type of job entails coordinating and booking vendors, book locations, schedule entertainment, and ensure everything goes off without a hitch and stays within the client’s budget. If you have any<em> </em>prior experience in event planning, or it is just something that genuinely interests you, then a work from home event planning job could be the <em>perfect match</em>!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>3. Virtual Assistant</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>Up to $29 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy social interaction, providing assistance, and working with a variety of clients, you might want to look into becoming a virtual assistant.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Virtual Assistants</strong> are responsible for responding to emails and phone calls, organizing meetings,scheduling travel accommodations, and attending to any other needs the client has.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One of the biggest benefits of being a remote virtual assistant is the ability to work with <em>multiple clients</em>. Many experienced virtual assistants take on 2 or 3 clients and work with both simultaneously, leading to <em>2 to 3 times the money</em>, and a full day’s work from the comfort of their home.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4. Amazon From Home</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None for entry level positions. <em>Additional experience and training may be required for mid and upper level positions.</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>Up to $32 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amazon from home jobs are one of the most unique work from home opportunities available right now, due to its extremely wide range of available positions. Amazon offers hundreds of jobs in any and every field you can imagine. Options range from<em> customer service</em> to <em>advertising and marketing specialists</em>, and everything in between!<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Working from home with Amazon is an amazing way to <em>make good money</em> and work a meaningful job for a massive company that is innovating and creating new opportunities each and every day.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5. Bookkeeping</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>No experience is required. <em>Online training courses and/or a certification are trouble-free and can increase your likelihood of landing clients.</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$20 to $36/hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you like numbers, making charts, and maintaining records, bookkeeping might be the perfect work from home job for you. Bookkeeping is a very profitable and flexible way to <strong>make a full time living</strong> or some extra cash on the side, and doesn’t require anything but some basic accounting skills and a computer.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bookkeeping jobs are especially abundant because of the nature of small businesses. Every small business needs a bookkeeper, and outsourcing the job to a remote bookkeeper is much more efficient than bringing on a full time employee.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Similar to being a virtual assistant, remote bookkeepers can take on multiple clients and make some serious money while doing so.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>6. Social Media Manager</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>No official experience required. <em>There are many viable online SMM certification and training courses you can do for free.</em><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$25 to $45 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social Media Management is a rapidly growing field in need of dedicated workers. Being a social media manager from home does not require any major experience or certifications, and if you currently use social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter, then you’re <em>already</em> a great candidate for a social media management position.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social Media Managers are responsible for running a companies social media platforms. That can mean daily or weekly posting, responding to comments, answering messages, and generally keeping the profiles up to date with the goals and needs of the company.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Many business owners <em>do not know how</em>, or simply <em>do not want</em> to run their companies social media presence and are looking for <strong>young, talented individuals</strong> to handle the task.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>7. Tech Support Representative</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$18 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the digital age, tech support representatives are needed now more than ever, and now you can do so <em>from the comfort of your home</em>. With the remote work movement expanding, tech support jobs have largely transitioned from call centers to remote and work from home opportunities.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tech support jobs are a great way to make a full-time living wage from home, or to make extra money on the side. As a tech support representative, you will be responsible for troubleshooting customer problems involving software, computers, phones, and any other form of tech the company sells. There are always<em> </em><em>full and part time positions available</em>, and the only things you need are a computer and a cell phone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>8. Writer</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$20 to $50 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a freelance writer, you can choose your specialty and interests from the start, and you can write primarily about subjects that interest <em>you</em>.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some of the major benefits of becoming a freelance writer:&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>The ability to work for multiple clients</li><li>The freedom to choose who you write for</li><li>The possibility of being brought on as a full time, work from home writer for a newspaper, blog site, or a research company.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once you land your first writing job, <em>it’s only up from there</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>9. Online Tutor</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>Bachelor’s degree in any subject is <em>typically</em> required<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$19 to $25<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Online tutoring jobs from home typically require applicants to have a Bachelor\'s degree, but each company’s requirements are different.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Online tutoring gives people the opportunity to work<strong> full or part time</strong> and typically has very flexible hours. Like many jobs on this list, as an online tutor you are able to take on multiple clients and clock a lot of hours if you want to.<em> The world is your oyster</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>10. Call Center Representative&nbsp;</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None. People who are fluent in more than one language do have an advantage 😉<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $18 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy engaging with others and providing assistance, being a call center representative may be the <em>perfect job</em> for you.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call center representatives are responsible for using their knowledge of the company products and services to assist customers with any questions, concerns, or problems they may have.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Work from home call center representative jobs are a consistent way for you to make some good money from the <em>comfort of your home</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>11. Travel Agent&nbsp;</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $21 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Travel agents are responsible for assisting clients in making travel plans, whether it’s for business or vacation.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Work from home travel agents are typically responsible for booking flights, rental cars, hotels, excursions, and providing a detailed outline of what a trip will consist of day to day. Travel agents can take on multiple clients, and are typically able to <em>work flexible hours</em> as a result.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>12. Blogger</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$13 to $22 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Blogging is one of the more risky jobs on this list. This job is a great way to earn some cash if you love writing, freedom, being your own boss, and taking risks. <em>Personal</em> and<em> professional</em> blogs have exploded in recent years, with new, <strong>successful blogs</strong> popping up each and every day.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy what you’re blogging about, you can treat it more like a side gig until it gets off the ground.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Starting your own blog has obvious risks involved because it can be tough getting your name out there and creating awareness for your new brand. But with consistent posts, passion for what you’re writing about, and a little luck, you can turn your personal blog into a fully monetized business capable of raking in that <strong>hard earned cash</strong>.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>13. Transcription</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $20 per hour<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Transcription is another viable option for anyone who enjoys typing, and wants the ability to work for multiple clients at once. Becoming a transcriptionist from home is an easy way to make some <em>side cash</em>, or, if you do want to take on multiple clients, it can become a full time work from home job. Transcriptionists are responsible for typing out a transcript for <strong>audio and video files</strong>, such as meeting videos, podcasts, and lectures.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you’d like to specialize in a certain field such as legal transcription, you could make even <em>more </em>money by becoming a full time transcriptionist within a few months!<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The work from home and remote worker movement is expanding every day. The reality is, these are just a few of our favorite work from home jobs. There is an endless amount of job opportunities available right now that will allow you to work at home. Take the skills you possess, the experience you’ve gained over the years, and relationships you’ve built to find the right opportunity for you! <strong>All you need to know is where to look.</strong> 😉<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','','','trash','closed','open','','__trashed','','','2019-07-08 14:54:11','2019-07-08 14:54:11','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000363',0,'post','',0),(100000364,2,'2019-07-08 13:31:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2019-07-08 13:31:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000364',0,'post','',0),(100000365,2,'2019-07-08 14:22:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2019-07-08 14:22:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000365',0,'post','',0),(100000366,2,'2019-07-08 14:50:50','2019-07-08 14:50:50','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Truck driving is an attractive career for adventure seekers that enjoy solo time and independent work.  It’s also great for people who want to make a healthy salary without needing secondary education. However, you do need <em>some </em>training before becoming a driver. Read on and discover what you need to know about Truck Driving School. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:more -->\n<!--more-->\n<!-- /wp:more -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?&amp;subaff4=truck%20driver\">Find Truck Driving Jobs Near You</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Depending on the industry and the trucking employer, you can make an annual salary of six figures as a truck driver.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That said, before you can find a job in the massive industry, you must receive your CDL certificate. In order for this to happen, you need to attend training school.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s important to understand the truck driving school process, and make sure to weigh your options. Ideally, you want the best quality education you can get for your money.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Be wary of hidden fees, such as obtaining permits, drug screening, insurance, and other items. You also want to enroll in a program that will ensure you a good job upon graduation.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>Truck Driving School</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a few different types of truck driver training.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Accredited schools: The Department of Education has approved the program. This means that is meets standard educational requirements</li><li>Certified programs: The Department of Transportation has approved the school based on set standards.</li><li>Licensed programs: The instructors, the curriculum and the facility have all met requirements set by the specific state.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is no uniform pricing for CDL training. Prospective students should be skeptical of “free” trainings. Put simply, you often get what you pay for. Private CDL schools can cost up to $10,000, but may offer smaller class sizes and better post-schooling employment help.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should ensure that tuition covers necessary supplies, extra help, classroom and over-the-road training. Further, employer-paid CDL training usually requires that you sign on for at least a year of working with that firm, many times at a lower salary than you may have been able to secure after schooling.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Instructors are professionals in the trucking industry.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>What Will I Learn?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While every CDL school is different, you can expect the first part of your program to take place in a classroom. You will focus on state and federal regulations, wider industry regulations, as well as records, logbooks and forms. Many schools offer night classes.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The other big piece of CDL training is the field segment of schooling. The Professional Truck Driver Institute Standard requires at least 44 hours of actual driving time. You will be accompanied by your instructor during these hours.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the field training, expect to familiarize yourself with pre- and post-trip inspections, trip planning and mapping, in-cab instruments and controls, safe driving practices, backing up, shifting, and more. Driving a commercial vehicle is much more involved than your traditional passenger car.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>How Hard is it to Pass Truck Driving School?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The CDL test includes a <a href=\"https://www.truckingtruth.com/trucking_blogs/Article-3541/passing-the-cdl-road-test-what-are-cdl-examiners-looking-for\">Road Test and a Knowledge Test.</a><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Common mistakes on the road test include turning too wide, and missing a shift. While these are acceptable mistakes, you should still avoid them. Mistakes that can cause an immediate fail include hitting curbs, rolling backward during a stop, and failing to check your mirrors.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The testing instructor will also be keeping an eye on your demeanor, and how you handle pressure. This person will have the final word about your testing verdict. It’s a good idea to build a friendly rapport with him or her off the bat. To pass the most common Class A CDL exam, you cannot have more than 30 points deducted from your total.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The CDL Knowledge Test quizzes you on your classroom learning. Expect specifics on topics like state rules and regulations, and weight limitations. The online test contains multiple choice questions. An 80% or higher will result in a pass.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should be sure to get plenty of practice in the days leading up to the test. Like any other exam, a good night’s sleep keeps your mind sharp.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>Truck Driving School requires a physical?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration requires that all interstate commercial motor vehicle drivers maintain a current Medical Examiner’s Certificate (MEC), Form MCSA-5876 to drive. Drivers will need to fill out the medical history section of the MER form. Once the exam is administered, it is valid for up to two years.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>What certification or licensing will I receive by graduating from School?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp; three main licensing classes for CDL school are CDL-A, B and C. The first is the most comprehensive out of the three. A Class A CDL allows you to operate a commercial vehicle with a trailer that weighs over 10,000 pounds. The combined weight of the vehicle and the trailer can exceed 26,001 pounds. The Class A license will give you authorization to operate most tractor-trailers, also known as semis and 18-wheelers.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next, you can add seven CDL Endorsements. Certain CDL schools allow for you to train for endorsements. For example, H endorsements allow you to drive commercial vehicles carrying hazardous materials.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No truck driving school can guarantee to get you a job upon passing your CDL and completing the program. That said, many of them offer hands on help in finding one.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Truck Driving School: What You Need to Know','','publish','closed','open','','truck-driving-school-what-you-need-to-know','','','2019-07-11 21:50:12','2019-07-11 21:50:12','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000366',0,'post','',0),(100000367,2,'2019-07-08 14:39:30','2019-07-08 14:39:30','','robson-hatsukami-morgan-NKr0qBAkU4s-unsplash','','inherit','closed','closed','','robson-hatsukami-morgan-nkr0qbaku4s-unsplash','','','2019-07-08 14:40:22','2019-07-08 14:40:22','',100000366,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/robson-hatsukami-morgan-NKr0qBAkU4s-unsplash.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100000368,5,'2019-07-08 17:20:11','2019-07-08 17:20:11','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=work%20from%20home\">Working from home</a> is an ideal way for millions of people to achieve the perfect work-life balance. With the world becoming more and more digital-dependent, the time to work from home is now. There are thousands of <a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=part%20time\">part-time</a> and <a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=full%20time\">full-time</a> opportunities available year round. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:more -->\n<!--more-->\n<!-- /wp:more -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Work from home jobs provide four unique attributes:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li><strong>Optimal flexibility</strong></li><li>The opportunity to work when you want (and even <em>where </em>you want!)</li><li>The ability to<strong> work from the comfort of your living room</strong></li><li>And a chance to skip your long morning commute. <br></li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>According to a 2017 study conducted by <a href=\"https://www.fundera.com\">FundEra.com</a>, <strong>86% of professionals</strong> said they are most productive when working alone. They also think a flexible, remote, or telecommuting job would make them more productive throughout the day. The study also detailed the most prominent reasons why job hunters are seeking work from home jobs. The leading reasons being scheduling flexibility, less distractions, higher wages, and the absence of office politics.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether you’re trying to save money or reduce stress, here are our<strong> Best Work from Home Jobs of 2019.&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>1. Product Tester</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$19 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Product Testing is one of the most fun and unique ways to make money from home. Product testing can involve testing <strong>makeup, video games, technology, food</strong>, and everything in between.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a work from home product tester, innovative, new products are sent right to your door for you to test. Typically, product testers are responsible for testing the product<em> in depth</em>. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>They then create a detailed<strong> report</strong> giving feedback on the product. Usually, the reports are geared towards the products appeal, usability, and overall usefulness. But the report requirements will be different depending on the product and&nbsp;company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=product%20tester\">Find Product Tester Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>2. Event Planner</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>Event planning certification (can be obtained via online courses)</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$22 per hour<br></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Event planning is one of the most <em>interesting</em> and <em>rewarding</em> work from home opportunities. However, you <em>do </em>need an event planning certification.  </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The good news is that there are plenty of viable online courses where you can obtain one in a few short weeks.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This type of job entails booking vendors and locations, scheduling entertainment, and more. Event planners must ensure everything goes off without a hitch. and stays within the client’s budget. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If Event Planning is just something that genuinely interests you, a work from home event planning job could be the <em>perfect match</em>!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=event%20planner\">Find Event Planner Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>3. Virtual Assistant</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>Up to $29 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy providing assistance, a lot of social interaction and working with multiple different clients, you should look into becoming a virtual assistant.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Virtual Assistants</strong> are typically responsible for answering emails and phone calls, scheduling and organizing meetings. They also plan travel arrangements such as flights and hotels.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A benefit being a work from home virtual assistant is the opportunity to work with <em>a variety of different clients</em>. Some of the more experienced virtual assistants take on 2 to 3 clients simultaneously. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Adding more clients gives you more work, which helps the days to fly by. It also allows you to double, or even <em>triple</em> your monthly income. All from the comfort of home!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=virtual%20assistant\">Find Virtual Assistant Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>4. Amazon From Home</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None for entry-level positions. <em>Additional experience and training may be required for mid and upper-level positions.</em></li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>Up to $32 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amazon from home has become one of the most sought after work from home jobs available right now. This is primarily due to the broad variety of positions available. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Amazon offers thousands of positions in any and every field imaginable. Mostly because there is a broad variety of skill levels that you can apply for. Opportunities include <em>customer service</em> jobs, <em>advertising and marketing specialists</em>, and even managerial positions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Working from home with Amazon is an exciting way to <em>make great money</em> and work a meaningful job. Amazon provides thousands of new work from home opportunities yearly. They are also constantly innovating and coming up with products that provide new, exciting career opportunities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=amazon%20work%20from%20home\">Find Amazon Work From Home Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>5. Bookkeeping</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>No experience is required. <em>Online training courses and/or a certification are trouble-free and can increase your likelihood of landing clients.</em> </li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$20 to $36/hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Do you like numbers? What about making charts and maintaining records? If you answered yes, bookkeeping could be the perfect job for you. Bookkeeping doesn’t require anything except for basic accounting skills and a computer. It seems like a viable way to make extra money, or even serve as a full time work from home career.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Similar to being a virtual assistant, remote bookkeepers can take on multiple clients and make some serious money while doing so.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bookkeeping jobs are consistently available because of the abundance of small businesses. Every small business needs a bookkeeper. Hiring on a full-time employee is more expensive than outsourcing the job to a work from home bookkeeper.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=remote%20bookkeeper\">Find Remote Bookkeeper Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>6. Social Media Manager</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>No official experience required. <em>There are many viable online SMM certification and training courses you can do for free.</em></li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$25 to $45 per hour<br></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because Social Media Management is a rapidly growing field in need of dedicated workers, you should consider it as a career. Being a social media manager from home does not require any major experience or certifications. Also, if you currently use social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter, then you’re <em>already</em> a great candidate for a social media management position.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Social Media Managers are responsible for running a companies social media platforms. That can mean daily or weekly posting, responding to comments, answering messages, and generally keeping the profiles up to date with the goals and needs of the company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Above all, many business owners <em>do not know how</em>, or simply <em>do not want</em> to run their companies social media presence. and are looking for <strong>young, talented individuals</strong> to handle the task.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=social%20media%20manager\">Find Social Media Manager Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>7. Tech Support Representative</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None </li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$18 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the digital age, tech support representatives are needed now more than ever, and now you can do so <em>from the comfort of your home</em>. With the remote work movement expanding, tech support jobs have largely transitioned from call centers to remote and work from home opportunities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tech support jobs are a great way to make a full-time living wage from home, or to make extra money on the side. As a tech support representative, you will be responsible for troubleshooting customer problems involving software, computers, phones, and any other form of tech the company sells. There are always<em> full and part-time positions available</em>, and the only things you need are a computer and a cell phone.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=remote%20tech%20support\">Find Tech Support Representative Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>8. Writer</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$20 to $50 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a freelance writer, you can choose your specialty and interests from the start, and you can write primarily about subjects that interest <em>you</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Here are some of the major benefits of becoming a freelance writer:&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>The ability to work for multiple clients</li><li>The freedom to choose who you write for</li><li>The possibility of being brought on as a full time, work from home writer for a newspaper, blog site, or a research company.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once you land your first writing job, <em>it’s only up from there</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=remote%20writer\">Find Remote Writing Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>9. Online Tutor</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>Bachelor’s degree in any subject is <em>typically</em> required </li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$19 to $25</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you’re passionate about education and learning, or you simply like to help people, online tutoring jobs are readily available and could be the perfect fit for you. Work from home tutoring jobs typically require applicants to have a Bachelor\'s degree, but each company’s requirements are different. The beauty of becoming a part or full-time online tutor is there are countless students who need help but don’t have time for or cannot afford the traditional tutoring methods, so there are always positions available in all sorts of topics.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Like a lot of jobs on this list, The world is your oyster in terms of scheduling. Online tutoring gives people the opportunity to work<strong> full or part-time</strong> and typically has very flexible hours, while also allowing you to take on multiple clients and make a very nice amount of money while doing so.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=online%20tutor\">Find Online Tutor Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>10. Call Center Representative&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None. People who are fluent in more than one language do have an advantage 😉</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $18 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy engaging with others and providing assistance, being a call center representative may be the <em>perfect job</em> for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Call center representatives are responsible for using their knowledge of the company products and services to assist customers with any questions, concerns, or problems they may have.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Finally, work from home call center representative jobs are a consistent way for you to make some good money from the <em>comfort of your home</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=remote%20call%20center\">Find Remote Call Center Representative Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>11. Travel Agent&nbsp;</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $21 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you have a knack for scheduling and planning and you have a passion for traveling, this could be the perfect opportunity for you! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Travel agents are usually responsible for assisting clients in making travel plans, whether it’s for business meetings, family visits, or a relaxing beach vacation, a travel agent’s help is always appreciated.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Work from home travel agents are tasked with for booking flights, rental cars, hotels, excursions, and providing a detailed outline of what a trip will consist of day-to-day. Travel agents can take on multiple clients, and are typically able to <em>work flexible hours</em> and rake in some good money as a result. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Not to mention, who doesn’t like working from the comfort of your own couch?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=travel%20agent\">Find Remote Travel Agent Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>12. Blogger</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$13 to $22 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Blogging is one of the more risky jobs on this list. This job is a great way to earn some cash if you love writing, freedom, being your own boss, and taking risks. <em>Personal</em> and<em> professional</em> blogs have exploded in recent years, with new, <strong>successful blogs</strong> popping up each and every day.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you enjoy what you’re blogging about, you can treat it more like a side gig until it gets off the ground.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Starting your own blog is difficult. Because getting your name out there and creating awareness for your new brand. But with consistent posts, passion for what you’re writing about, and a little luck, you can turn your personal blog into a fully monetized business capable of raking in that <strong>hard earned cash</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=blogger\">Find Blogger Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>13. Transcription</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Experience Required: </strong>None</li><li><strong>Average Pay: </strong>$15 to $20 per hour</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Summary:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Transcription is another great option for anyone who enjoys typing, and is seeking the ability to work flexible hours. The barrier to entry for transcription jobs is essentially nothing, all you need is a computer or laptop and a comfy chair to sit in while you type. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Becoming a work from home transcriptionist is an easy way to make some <em>side cash</em>, or, if you do want to take on multiple clients, it can become a full-time job. Transcriptionists are usually responsible for typing out a multiple page transcript for <strong>audio and video files</strong>, such as meeting videos, podcasts, and lectures.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you’d like to specialize in a certain field such as legal transcription or medical transcription, you could make even <em>more </em>money by becoming a full time transcriptionist within a few short months!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=remote%20transcription\">Find Remote Transcription Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>In conclusion..</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The work from home and remote worker movement is expanding every day. Furthermore, these are just a few of our favorite work from home jobs. There is an endless amount of job opportunities available right now that will allow you to work at home. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Take the skills you possess, the experience you’ve gained over the years, and relationships you’ve built to find the right opportunity for you! <strong>All you need to know is where to look.</strong> 😉<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Best Work From Home Opportunities in 2019','','publish','closed','open','','best-work-from-home-opportunities-in-2019','','','2019-07-11 21:50:17','2019-07-11 21:50:17','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000368',0,'post','',0),(100000369,2,'2019-07-08 15:00:55','2019-07-08 15:00:55','work from home opportunities are changing the way we make money. ','thought-catalog-Nv-vx3kUR2A-unsplash','','inherit','closed','closed','','thought-catalog-nv-vx3kur2a-unsplash','','','2019-07-08 16:01:22','2019-07-08 16:01:22','',100000368,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/thought-catalog-Nv-vx3kUR2A-unsplash.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100000370,2,'2019-07-08 17:31:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','closed','open','','','','','2019-07-08 17:31:00','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000370',0,'post','',0),(100000372,2,'2019-07-08 19:41:42','2019-07-08 19:41:42','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Truck drivers can earn a healthy living without needing higher education. In fact, top truck driving jobs can pay an annual salary in the six-figure range. Because of these reasons, we\'ve detailed how to become a truck driver in some detail!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:more -->\n<!--more-->\n<!-- /wp:more -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That said, truck driving isn’t for everyone. There are certain requirements and tests that you must pass before you can qualify for most jobs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=truck%20driving\">Find Truck Driving Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For one, the most obvious need for truck drivers, is that you must enjoy driving. Driving for long periods of time requires a high level of patience. Willingness to sit still for hours at a time is key. Given a majority of truck driving jobs are one-person gigs, you must be okay with spending time alone. Self-motivation in this career will differentiate the best truck drivers, since hlj manage yourself.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being a “good driver,” and following all safety procedures is paramount as well. Driving any type of vehicle comes with its own risk. Operating oversized pieces of heavy equipment poses even more of a hazard on the road.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before taking up trucking, ensure you are in good physical condition. While bodybuilder shape isn\'t required, you should be able to move around equipment and perform other physical tasks. Staying alcohol and drug free is a rule for truck driving, as tests come at random. The legal alcohol limit for a CDL holding individual is 0.04, half of what it is for the rest of the population. Any trace of alcohol will get you a 24 hour out of service order.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>The Lifestyle of a Truck Driver</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For those that prefer solitude and can manage their own schedule, truck driving could offer a nice lifestyle.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Becoming a truck driver can offer a life of adventure compared to a typical desk job. Many drivers are able to see more of our beautiful countryside than they could have imagined. Also, although truck driving itself for the most part is an individual job, many in the industry find a strong sense of camaraderie with other truckers.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On the flip side, it’s important to note the unique challenges that come with the career. These include potential issues with having a family. Most jobs require weeks on the job at a time, with much of it spend alone on the road.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trucking can be extremely difficult for families and relationships. This is why the divorce rate among truck drivers is much higher than the national average. Your kids, spouse, or partner must be okay with you away for months at a time. If this isn\'t the case, you may carefully weigh whether a career in truck driving is worth the cost to your personal life.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Truck Driving School</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you want to pursue a career in trucking after all, you will need to enroll in a truck driving school to receive your Commercial Driver’s License (CDL). This license allows you to operate large, heavy or hazardous material vehicles in commerce.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">Related Article<br><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/guides/how-to-get-a-commercial-drivers-license-cdl/\">How to get a Commercial Driver\'s License (CDL)</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To receive your CDL, you must have a state-issued driver’s license, meet age requirements, and have a clean record. There is a knowledge exam and a skills test.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Going to CDL school does not require that you pay all expenses out of pocket. You may be eligible for financial aid in the form of scholarships, grants and loans. States provide grant money from the FMCSA. Grants are also awarded under the Workforce Investment Act and the Trade Adjustment Assistance (TAA) grant. Loans are available under FAFSA for certain schools with longer programs. Military veterans may also receive funding under the GI Bill. Certain companies provide varying levels of financial aid due to a shortage of workers in high-demand industries.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Finding a Truck Driving Job after Driving School</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If you were not funded by a trucking company that sponsored your training in exchange for a work commitment, your next step is to look for a job.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Most large truck stops have a hiring magazine rack with free publications that specialize in types of drivers or owner operators. Most will have their hiring and operating areas shown on a map in the ad. You will need to consider whether you want to work for a local and regional operator. These will keep you closer to home but&nbsp; pay less than a national operator, which on average carries more freight.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">Related Article<br><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/guides/10-best-truck-driving-jobs-for-earning-serious-cash/\">10 Best Truck Driving Jobs for Earning Serious Cash</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Once you decide on possibles companies to work for, it’s important to have conversations with current and past employees and a recruiter. While browsing online will help, hanging out at a truck stop when drivers make their stops at night is a great call.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>On-the-job Training for Truck Drivers</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Different companies will offer different training deals, although it is rarely free. Most will require a one-year work commitment, and will credit a part of the training cost per week. Depending on the school, you may or may not have to pay for your own room and meals during training.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CDL training will cover technical driving skills, mechanical aspects of trucks, navigation, maps, log books, permits, etc. Once you are hired, you will spend anywhere from a day to a couple of weeks in orientation.&nbsp; You may also go through additional training. A company may pair you up with another more experienced driver for a period of time for mentorship.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\">Related Article<br><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/guides/truck-driving-school-what-you-need-to-know/\">Truck Driving School: What You Need to Know</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><strong>Now that you’re a trained Truck Driver, how much money can you make?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A typical starting salary for a truck driving job is around $30,000. Experience, as well as specialization and employment with a good trucking company can increase your salary.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In 2017, the top 10% of truck drivers brought home over $64,000. The median yearly salary of truck drivers was $42,480, per a report by<a href=\"https://www.truckerstraining.com/how-much-do-truck-drivers-make-ultimate-guide/\"> Trucker’s Training</a>. Out of 4,230 salaries reported on<a href=\"https://www.glassdoor.com/Salaries/us-truck-driver-salary-SRCH_IL.0,2_IN1_KO3,15.htm\"> Glassdoor</a>, the average base pay for truck drivers in the United States is $57,872 per year.\n\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?subaff4=truck%20driving\">Find Truck Driving Jobs</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Become a Truck Driver: a Simple Guide','','publish','closed','open','','become-a-truck-driver-a-simple-guide','','','2019-07-11 21:41:44','2019-07-11 21:41:44','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?p=100000372',0,'post','',0),(100000373,2,'2019-07-08 19:27:59','2019-07-08 19:27:59','Learn how to become a truck driver in easy steps','dynamic-transit-co-0Rr25gWxxLs-unsplash','','inherit','closed','closed','','dynamic-transit-co-0rr25gwxxls-unsplash','','','2019-07-08 19:28:23','2019-07-08 19:28:23','',100000372,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/dynamic-transit-co-0Rr25gWxxLs-unsplash.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100000380,2,'2019-07-09 21:42:25','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html\" charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta property=\"fb:app_id\" content=\"424426844274364\">\n\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/giveaways\">\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\">\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Enter for a chance to win a&nbsp;complete Resume and Cover Letter Overhaul&nbsp;from experts that know your industry!\">\n\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Enter for a chance to win a&nbsp;complete Resume and Cover Letter Overhaul&nbsp;from experts that know your industry!\">\n<meta property=\"fb:admins\" content=\"1088490351\">\n<meta property=\"fb:admins\" content=\"11512735\">\n<meta property=\"fb:admins\" content=\"1088490312\">\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Three lucky winners will be able to apply to jobs with confidence that only professional help can give. Industry experts will work with you to create a compelling, perfectly formatted resume and cover letter. This service offered by TopResume.com typically costs $219, but we\'re giving away them for FREE.&nbsp;\">\n<title>Enter for a chance to win a&nbsp;complete Resume and Cover Letter Overhaul&nbsp;from experts that know your industry!</title>\n\n<style type=\"text/css\">\nbody { border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0; }<br />\n</style><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width\">\n<meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-capable\" content=\"yes\">\n<div id=\"vsscript_53972_443464\"></div>\n<script async=\"\" type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://app.viralsweep.com/vsa-full-12ff8e-53972.js?sid=53972_443464\"></script>','Giveaways','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-07-09 21:42:25','2019-07-09 21:42:25','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?page_id=100000380',0,'page','',0),(100000382,2,'2019-07-11 21:44:13','0000-00-00 00:00:00','<p>[vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" bb_tab_container=\"\"][vc_column][vc_basic_grid post_type=\"post\" max_items=\"3\" style=\"lazy\" items_per_page=\"20\" order=\"ASC\" grid_id=\"vc_gid:1562880841648-e206470d-9ea5-5\" bb_tab_container=\"\" taxonomies=\"69\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_wp_categories][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\n','Blog | Career Advice, Tips & Topics of Interest','','draft','closed','closed','','blog','','','2019-07-11 21:44:13','2019-07-11 21:44:13','',0,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/?page_id=100000382',0,'page','',0),(100000383,2,'2019-07-11 21:24:12','2019-07-11 21:24:12','','chris-liverani-9cd8qOgeNIY-unsplash','','inherit','closed','closed','','chris-liverani-9cd8qogeniy-unsplash','','','2019-07-11 21:24:12','2019-07-11 21:24:12','',100000382,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/chris-liverani-9cd8qOgeNIY-unsplash.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100000384,2,'2019-07-11 21:30:10','2019-07-11 21:30:10','','glenn-carstens-peters-npxXWgQ33ZQ-unsplash','','inherit','closed','closed','','glenn-carstens-peters-npxxwgq33zq-unsplash','','','2019-07-11 21:30:10','2019-07-11 21:30:10','',100000382,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/glenn-carstens-peters-npxXWgQ33ZQ-unsplash.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(100000387,2,'2019-07-11 21:55:33','2019-07-11 21:55:33','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Truck driving is an attractive career for adventure seekers that enjoy solo time and independent work.  It’s also great for people who want to make a healthy salary without needing secondary education. However, you do need <em>some </em>training before becoming a driver. Read on and discover what you need to know about Truck Driving School. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:more -->\n<!--more-->\n<!-- /wp:more -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"backgroundColor\":\"very-light-gray\"} -->\n<p style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"has-background has-very-light-gray-background-color\"><a href=\"https://www.finddreamjobs.com/jobs/?&amp;subaff4=truck%20driver\">Find Truck Driving Jobs Near You</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Depending on the industry and the trucking employer, you can make an annual salary of six figures as a truck driver.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>That said, before you can find a job in the massive industry, you must receive your CDL certificate. In order for this to happen, you need to attend training school.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s important to understand the truck driving school process, and make sure to weigh your options. Ideally, you want the best quality education you can get for your money.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Be wary of hidden fees, such as obtaining permits, drug screening, insurance, and other items. You also want to enroll in a program that will ensure you a good job upon graduation.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>Truck Driving School</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There are a few different types of truck driver training.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Accredited schools: The Department of Education has approved the program. This means that is meets standard educational requirements</li><li>Certified programs: The Department of Transportation has approved the school based on set standards.</li><li>Licensed programs: The instructors, the curriculum and the facility have all met requirements set by the specific state.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is no uniform pricing for CDL training. Prospective students should be skeptical of “free” trainings. Put simply, you often get what you pay for. Private CDL schools can cost up to $10,000, but may offer smaller class sizes and better post-schooling employment help.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should ensure that tuition covers necessary supplies, extra help, classroom and over-the-road training. Further, employer-paid CDL training usually requires that you sign on for at least a year of working with that firm, many times at a lower salary than you may have been able to secure after schooling.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Instructors are professionals in the trucking industry.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>What Will I Learn?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>While every CDL school is different, you can expect the first part of your program to take place in a classroom. You will focus on state and federal regulations, wider industry regulations, as well as records, logbooks and forms. Many schools offer night classes.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The other big piece of CDL training is the field segment of schooling. The Professional Truck Driver Institute Standard requires at least 44 hours of actual driving time. You will be accompanied by your instructor during these hours.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In the field training, expect to familiarize yourself with pre- and post-trip inspections, trip planning and mapping, in-cab instruments and controls, safe driving practices, backing up, shifting, and more. Driving a commercial vehicle is much more involved than your traditional passenger car.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>How Hard is it to Pass Truck Driving School?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The CDL test includes a <a href=\"https://www.truckingtruth.com/trucking_blogs/Article-3541/passing-the-cdl-road-test-what-are-cdl-examiners-looking-for\">Road Test and a Knowledge Test.</a><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Common mistakes on the road test include turning too wide, and missing a shift. While these are acceptable mistakes, you should still avoid them. Mistakes that can cause an immediate fail include hitting curbs, rolling backward during a stop, and failing to check your mirrors.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The testing instructor will also be keeping an eye on your demeanor, and how you handle pressure. This person will have the final word about your testing verdict. It’s a good idea to build a friendly rapport with him or her off the bat. To pass the most common Class A CDL exam, you cannot have more than 30 points deducted from your total.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The CDL Knowledge Test quizzes you on your classroom learning. Expect specifics on topics like state rules and regulations, and weight limitations. The online test contains multiple choice questions. An 80% or higher will result in a pass.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You should be sure to get plenty of practice in the days leading up to the test. Like any other exam, a good night’s sleep keeps your mind sharp.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>Truck Driving School requires a physical?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Federal Motor Carrier Safety Administration requires that all interstate commercial motor vehicle drivers maintain a current Medical Examiner’s Certificate (MEC), Form MCSA-5876 to drive. Drivers will need to fill out the medical history section of the MER form. Once the exam is administered, it is valid for up to two years.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2><br><strong>What certification or licensing will I receive by graduating from School?</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp; three main licensing classes for CDL school are CDL-A, B and C. The first is the most comprehensive out of the three. A Class A CDL allows you to operate a commercial vehicle with a trailer that weighs over 10,000 pounds. The combined weight of the vehicle and the trailer can exceed 26,001 pounds. The Class A license will give you authorization to operate most tractor-trailers, also known as semis and 18-wheelers.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next, you can add seven CDL Endorsements. Certain CDL schools allow for you to train for endorsements. For example, H endorsements allow you to drive commercial vehicles carrying hazardous materials.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>No truck driving school can guarantee to get you a job upon passing your CDL and completing the program. That said, many of them offer hands on help in finding one.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Truck Driving School: What You Need to Know','','inherit','closed','closed','','100000366-autosave-v1','','','2019-07-11 21:55:33','2019-07-11 21:55:33','',100000366,'https://www.finddreamjobs.com/uncategorized/100000366-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
